"{\n    \"explanation\": \"The paper focuses on the prediction of diabetic foot risk using artificial intelligence, specifically examining the application of machine learning techniques like SVM and KNN to identify patients at risk of developing diabetic foot complications. This aligns most closely with the management and complications of type 2 diabetes, given the prevalence of diabetic foot as a complication and the use of AI for risk prediction.\",\n    \"class_labels\": [\"type_2_diabetes\"]\n}"